						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1476: 1554 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This damaged inscription is dated Śaka 1476, [Ānanda], [dvādaśi], which details are not sufficient for verification.</p>						

						<p>It seems to record some gift to provide for the food-offerings to the goddess Aṅgāḷamma by a <hi rend="italic">nāyaka,</hi> whose name is lost.</p>						

